 she cried silently, falling through an infinite pit of shame.&nbsp; Farmer Jigger’s face rose in her mind.&nbsp; She shuddered and leapt up as if the bed had burst into flames.&nbsp; She dressed quickly, almost unable to breathe, and fled the mansion, her legs burning.</span>
