Laurence shook his head, feeling that to follow these thoughts was to attempt to ford an infinite river.&nbsp; Personality is little more than a limitation of perspective.&nbsp; Laurence, in widening his senses, was losing himself, and that felt close enough to madness to be resisted with all the wan strength of his fading will.</span>
</p>

<p style=&quot;text-align:left;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:avoid;line-height:200%;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:14.4pt;&quot;>
