&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
<span lang=&quot;en-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;text-transform:none;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;line-height:200%;&quot;>
It was imperative that witnesses be produced, for if Mary had incited the riot, she could be convicted for that offense – an offense that could carry the death penalty, at the court’s discretion</span>
</p>

<p style=&quot;text-align:left;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:avoid;line-height:200%;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;&quot;>
