At Laurence’s protestation that the county would no longer accept her authority, Stephen and Jack remained mute, clearly indicating that such matters were beyond their concern.&nbsp; The twins conscripted Father Jones to scour the village and try to find any souls who remained above-ground who had been part of the previous night’s conflagration.&nbsp; Laurence sent word to Orson Andrews to bring Mary to the village for transport to London.</span>
</p>

<p style=&quot;text-align:left;page-break-inside:auto;page-break-after:auto;page-break-before:avoid;line-height:200%;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;>
